<ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Vienna</ENAMEX>, <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Paris</ENAMEX>, and <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">Berlin</ENAMEX>, tickets can cost twice as much and contribute an
even smaller share of operating budgets. I'll get to the question of why opera
