<ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">European</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE_DESC">countries</ENAMEX>, the instinctive reply is "the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG_DESC">government</ENAMEX>." But even in
