the most <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">needy</ENAMEX> of the fine arts, it is also the most elitist. In the <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">United</ENAMEX>
<ENAMEX TYPE="GPE_DESC">States</ENAMEX>, according to a just-published survey of participation in the arts,
