reputation in <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE">England</ENAMEX> was not helped <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">a couple of years ago</TIMEX> when a <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">Tory</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">minister</ENAMEX>
