<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">enthusiasts</ENAMEX> in this <ENAMEX TYPE="GPE_DESC">country</ENAMEX> constantly lament the lack of direct government
support for the arts. <ENAMEX TYPE="NATIONALITY">Europeans</ENAMEX>, on the other hand, faced with a new climate of
