            Those hoping to reduce costs run smack up against <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">Baumol</ENAMEX>'s
Law, named for the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">economist</ENAMEX> <ENAMEX TYPE="PERSON">William Baumol</ENAMEX>, who first elaborated it in a <TIMEX TYPE="DATE">1966</TIMEX>
